-- Impala Platinum Restarts Shaft No. 11 in South Africa After a Suspension
-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 2010-11-08T09:57:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/impala-platinum-restarts-shaft-no-11-in-south-africa-after-a-suspension.html
Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd. resumed
production at its Number 11 shaft in South Africa today after a
fatal accident on Nov. 1 suspended work in the area.  The production loss was “minimal,” Bob Gilmour, a
spokesman for the company said by phone from Johannesburg today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  